<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A̱ Kenan achukma ƲIT158</title>
<aka>Canaan., Kenan.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba yakni hoyo lishke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 A̱ki i̱ yakni pulla ka,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C1]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V2]
 Ho minti̱, Chisʋs ʋt achi,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 Ona li pulla chi̱ hoke;
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C2]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V3]
 Chisʋs ilʋppak pullʋshke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 Hoho̱yo li pulla chi̱shke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke

[C3]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V4]
 Aiachukma hoho̱yo lishke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 Ayukpa hoho̱yo lishke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C4]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V5]
 Ʋm ʋlla 't tikba ia tok,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 A̱ kana 't tikba ia tok,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C5]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V6]
 Sa tikba ish ona hokmʋt,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 Mihintishke, ish achashke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C6]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.

[V7]
 Momʋt il ia pullashke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
 Aiokcha̱ya yakni yoke,
 Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke:

[C7]
   A̱ Kenan achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke,
   A̱ Kenan, a̱ yakni achukma,
   Kenan ia hosh a̱ya lishke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>158</hymn_number>
</song>